metadata.description: "Ride Inside" is a high-energy breakbeat track that captures the intense and fierce vibe of city life at night. This track is the perfect accompaniment to a night out on the town, whether you're listening to it in your headphones or feeling it on the dance floor in the midst of an electrifying DJ set. With its driving beats and pulsing basslines, this track will transport you to the heart of the city, where anything can happen and the party never stops. Get ready to ride the wave of this exhilarating track and let its infectious rhythms carry you away.
metadata.name: Ride Inside #1
metadata.title: Ride Inside
